Hoist stood on Sludge's back, trying to gain footing. His device on his
back jutted up a bit, then scanned Sludge's head area. "Now come on
Slag, is that anyway to treat your fellow Dinobot?" he asked jovialy,
rather finding this situation humorous himself.
